<p class="rich-text block-editor-rich-text__editable wp-block-paragraph" role="textbox" contenteditable="true" aria-multiline="true" aria-label="Paragraph block">By the way, if you happen to know a good Indian restaurant, please let me know, cheers!</p>

</div>
